\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"唔係因為善果而種善因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473eeb4b4b609152f84cc7f0871c50b2adb1f434","tid":2515011,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"如果因果報應唔係真 咁我妄語有咩好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cb15b50b60fb31871c8ff751c9ade0e5d4608d","tid":2515011,"uid":238475,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T16:01:23.000Z","msg":"佛從來無講過善有善報，只有 &quot;因果輪迴&quot; 。"},{"pid":"f7b1225f82aa5f0a764874fb482db66a7c23cca0","tid":2515011,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a4f79b78c77d825e35b0d4c42ab8f1a6ecfcecf6","tid":2515011,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"766aa430e3f240789909f67dbf8e2352b9b1c116","tid":2515011,"uid":229789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"有咩衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:39:46.000Z","msg":"佛教徒肯定自己講嘅嘢係真。咁佢點解咁肯定自己講嘅嘢係真，種善因得善果係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T16:05:35.000Z","msg":"雖然佛學冇善有善報，但都有輪迴<br />\n<br />\n修行人通過四禪八定之後證得諸多神通<br />\n用嗰啲神通自然可以得知輪迴係咩一回事<br />\n所以唔算妄語<br />\n<br />\n至於一個未受過現代科學教育嘅佛教徒可能由細到大都剩係聽過佛學<br />\n對佢地嘅世界觀信到十足十 咁都唔會有妄語<br />\n<br />\n至於未證得神通但又受過現代科學教育人嘅佛教徒同你講輪迴? 佢地一係白癡到唔明現代科學，一係日日妄語"},{"pid":"3d1942f8d82f537b096147eb43e63116bbcda964","tid":2515011,"uid":69866,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T16:06:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://daimones.blogspot.com/2012/10/unfalsifiable.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdaimones.blogspot.com%2F2012%2F10%2Funfalsifiable.html%3Fm%3D1&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=9cac369e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://daimones.blogspot.com/2012/10/unfalsifiable.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"8b8f169238a772cef07e7031b0e7b128dbfeb2b2","tid":2515011,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"咁佛教徒未見過佛陀添, 咁引述佛陀說話係咪又係妄語"},{"pid":"1f5969b9e97871ca8afea4482e2cecfe552d8cae","tid":2515011,"uid":121355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>《善見律毘婆沙》：「妄語者，<strong>口與心相違</strong>，亦名空語也；<strong>不犯者，欲說此，誤說彼</strong>。妄語戒廣說竟，此是性罪。」<br />\n<br />\n《雜阿含&middot;一〇三九經》：「不實妄語，或於王家、真實言家、多眾聚集，求當言處，作不實說，<strong>不見言見，見言不見，不聞言聞，聞言不聞，知言不知，不知言知</strong>，<strong>因自因他，或因財利</strong>，知而妄語，而不捨離，是名妄語。」</blockquote><br />\n當中強調嘅係某人存有欺騙嘅意圖，然後講任何與其主觀體驗<strong>或</strong>認知不符嘅話語，先會構成妄語<br />\n放返喺呢個情況，除非某人謊稱自己睇到業報嘅實際運作，否則並不構成妄語"},{"pid":"a67163e165a64cb3d7d3b40d727707d2ecd39fc5","tid":2515011,"uid":33609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"業力不可思異<br />\n呢d 因果報唔係佢地會解釋嘅範疇"},{"pid":"be756d4449cada337d72620470994c8bab4eb202","tid":2515011,"uid":102640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b8f169238a772cef07e7031b0e7b128dbfeb2b2","tid":2515011,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"咁佛教徒未見過佛陀添, 咁引述佛陀說話係咪又係妄語"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:09:35.000Z","msg":"佛陀嘅說話係法身<br />\n點會係妄語？"},{"pid":"e9941735895cb66625ddbe2835297fa5206a8cd1","tid":2515011,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be756d4449cada337d72620470994c8bab4eb202","tid":2515011,"uid":102640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b8f169238a772cef07e7031b0e7b128dbfeb2b2","tid":2515011,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"咁佛教徒未見過佛陀添, 咁引述佛陀說話係咪又係妄語"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:09:35.000Z","msg":"佛陀嘅說話係法身<br />\n點會係妄語？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T21:19:50.000Z","msg":"咪話唔係囉<br />\n我未見過一尊菩薩棟喺我面前顯靈，唔通我話有菩薩存在又係妄語嗎？我真心相信有，唔係證實到有<br />\n所以回樓主，妄語係叫人唔好講大話呃人、唔好吹水唔識扮識，而唔係乜都要確切證實到有先講得"},{"pid":"ad9b5554d520b3e2c157c41e80e3dc7fa1bae5cc","tid":2515011,"uid":199145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04be9c88eeccd399b747a0f83b8695301df4dee8","tid":2515011,"uid":36435,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:42:23.000Z","msg":"點解成日要用理性黎argue宗教鳩up野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T22:56:50.000Z","msg":"聽過Theistic rationalism未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2227b0ab51f283437fd43d091bc6fa4b419305","tid":2515011,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9941735895cb66625ddbe2835297fa5206a8cd1","tid":2515011,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be756d4449cada337d72620470994c8bab4eb202","tid":2515011,"uid":102640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b8f169238a772cef07e7031b0e7b128dbfeb2b2","tid":2515011,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"咁佛教徒未見過佛陀添, 咁引述佛陀說話係咪又係妄語"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:09:35.000Z","msg":"佛陀嘅說話係法身<br />\n點會係妄語？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T21:19:50.000Z","msg":"咪話唔係囉<br />\n我未見過一尊菩薩棟喺我面前顯靈，唔通我話有菩薩存在又係妄語嗎？我真心相信有，唔係證實到有<br />\n所以回樓主，妄語係叫人唔好講大話呃人、唔好吹水唔識扮識，而唔係乜都要確切證實到有先講得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T23:49:43.000Z","msg":"唔確切證實到有先講，同吹水唔識扮識有咩分別？"},{"pid":"bdb17531261043f178e6bd554155171c13d32f32","tid":2515011,"uid":67425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e2227b0ab51f283437fd43d091bc6fa4b419305","tid":2515011,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9941735895cb66625ddbe2835297fa5206a8cd1","tid":2515011,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be756d4449cada337d72620470994c8bab4eb202","tid":2515011,"uid":102640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T20:09:35.000Z","msg":"佛陀嘅說話係法身<br />\n點會係妄語？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T21: